zm_airport_panic_bobpoblo2

  Zombies have attacked the local city and some residents have taken hold inside the airport. The zombies soon attacked from behind the Airport coming from the runway and over took the back side of the Airport. Get ready the zombies are coming!

Unfortunately the original no longer works after the patch.  I had to make several changes to update the map to work with the latest patch. Please enjoy! 

The map is a lot smaller now because I deleted most of the back half of the Airport. I also added more spots in the front section.

- 64 Spawns
- 3d Skybox
- Cubemaps
- Optimized even more for better FPS
- Plenty more secret spots
- Overview radar map
- Soundscapes
- Buy Zones

Secret spots include: vents, illusionary walls, teleport locations and breakable walls.

Many things have been changed and added into this second version, a few things include:
Added some more connector vents to speed up getting around the map.
Removed one of the two planes from the 3d skybox in order to reduce skybox lag.
Made dozens of ‘tweaks’ to camping spots, both with cades and no cades.
Widened the door on the plane.
Added multiple Soundscapes
Removed some props and added others in various locations around the map.
All breakable glass that was previously set to 5,000HP has now been reduced to 1,000-1,5000HP.
Modified most crouch spots to be more balanced/ less overpowered for humans.

And many more changes that I won’t list.

This is the Second version, please enjoy, comment and rate!

-==READ EVERYTHING PLEASE==-

IMPORTANT FOR ADMINS: 4way_spacetunnel is a BIG map. If you want people to be able to download the map directly from your server, you must use this command:

net_maxfilesize 52

Default 16mb. 4way_spacetunnel is 49.7mb.

Without this command changed to 52, people will not be able to download it and will get an error message like "Map zm_4way_spacetunnel_idm_v2.bsp is missing". 

----->If your server BZIPs the map you're ok.

Map Information:

Filesize: 49.7 mb 
Spawnpoints: 72 
Special Features: 1 spaceships, no fall damage 
Custom Textures Used: yes
Custom Sounds Used: yes

INSTALLATION:

Copy the cstrike folder into your "".../steam/steamapps/username/counter-strike source/" folder. Click yes to all and you're done.


A couple of features:
- No fall damage!
- New elevators
- New buildings.
- Well balanced spots, not impossible for zombies though not too easy.
- Totally retextured.! Lot's of custom textures used,
- 72 (!) spawn points for big servers
- Much bigger spawn area
- Advanced Teleporters (make the map faster)
- New elevator system instead of the old crane

* And much much more.


PS. I used the old screenshots from v1 ;)

Spacetunnel remake made by: [ZFC] idm

Some of the most used textures made by: [ZFC] Satch

Filesize: 54 mb

Special Features: 2 spaceships (1 drivable), no fall damage

Custom Sounds Used: yes
------------------------------

INSTALLATION:
-----------------

Copy the cstrike folder into your "".../steam/steamapps/username/counter-strike source/"
folder. Click yes to all and you are done.

IMPORTANT: This map uses a point_servercommand to set sv_turbophysics to 0. Otherwise
you won't be able to fly in the little spaceship. When your server has banned "point_servercommand" then use the cfg file that is packed into the rar file.

--------------------------------------------------------------
A couple of features:

* 2 Spaceships! And one of those you can drive yourself!
* No fall damage!
* New elevators
* New buildings.
* Well balanced spots, not impossible for zombies and not to easy
* 1 "secret" where you can blow up the drivable spaceship with. 
(opens 3 minutes after someone got into the spaceship
* Totally retextured.! Lot's of custom textures used,
* 72 (!) spawn points for big servers
* Much bigger spawn area
* Advanced Teleporters (make the map faster)
* New elevator system in stead of the old crane
* And much much more.

Backstory:

Scientist's log 12/30: Today marks a great triumph. We have synthesized a stable virus that can be used to extend the life human beings. There will be plenty of celebration tonight!

Scientist's log 12/31: That bumbling idiot Jone's acidently broke one of the viles containing the virus during last nights party at the office. We put him in the quaruntine room for punishment.

Scientist's log 1/2: Everyone went home early due to new years, and it appears we left Jones in the quaruntine room the whole time... the boss will have our heads for this one... but I can't shake the feeling that Jones is acting a little strange, maybe we should leave him in there a little longer

Scientist's log 1/9: Things have turned a bit grim at the office, ever since Jones started... changing. We need to run more tests on the virus it seems...

Scientist's log 1/10: there was a significant change to Jones's condition today, he's turned violent and his vital signs are... different... I don't know how to describe it. Good thing we accidentally quaruntined him for this long.

Scientist's log 1/15: It was under control.. we were safe.. but now it's out.... the terrorists.. they knew somehow. . . They broke in and released it! They just kept coming.. and coming, we didn't stand a chance... just too many... There was a slaughter, but I was able to escape into the caf and make a barricade... I hope someone get's this before it's too lat- oh no, it found me... but that's not Jones... no not human... I need the containment team now! Help me- oh god NOOOOOOOO- *static*
